## IRC

### Connect to a server

/connect irc.freenode.net

### Set a nickname 

/nick tarnacious

### Use an existing nick from the server

/msg NickServe tarnacious <password>

### Password recover via mail 

/msg NickServe SENDPASS tarnacious

### join a channel

/join nixos

### ignore some noice

/ignore * joins parts quits

or

/ignore -channels #flowtype * JOINS PARTS QUITS NICKS

### switching between channels

<ALT>+<number>

### scroll up

<Fn>+<up/down arrow>

### Logging

/SET autolog ON
